ount\n```\n\nThis solution iterates over each possible starting index `i` of a subarray in `nums` that could match the `pattern`. For each starting index, it checks if the subarray `nums[i..i+m]` matches the `pattern` by comparing the elements according to the rules specified in the pattern. If a match is found, it increments the `count`. Finally, it returns the total count of matching subarrays.", "estimated_date": 1707609600000}